data.title: Cn32-2 - 2013-07 Container Securing
data.meta_description: Cn32-2_2013-07 Container Securing - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides guidelines for classifying container securing arrangements on ships. It outlines procedures for analyzing container securing under various loading conditions using either direct beam calculations or formula-based methods. Acceptance criteria are defined for containers, securing devices, and ship structures. The document has been updated from the previous version with revised design loads, acceptance criteria, and additional guidance for analyzing mixed container stacks and non-standard arrangements.
